Hermes Gizmo
============

Hermes Gizmo is derived from Hermes Tool Slimmer by the Hermes Tool Slimmer
contributors. The upstream project is available at:

    https://github.com/alias8818/hermes-tool-slimmer

This fork keeps the upstream MIT license. The upstream copyright notice and
MIT permission notice are preserved in LICENSE and must be included in all
copies or substantial portions of the software.

Hermes Gizmo adds compatibility aliases, diagnostics, dashboard refinements,
state-migration planning, and other changes maintained by the Hermes Gizmo
contributors.
